Package: conformalForecast
Title: Conformal prediction methods for multistep-ahead time series forecasting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Xiaoqian", "Wang", , "Xiaoqian.Wang@monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4827-496X"))
Description: Methods and tools for performing multistep-ahead time series forecasting
             using conformal prediction methods including classical conformal prediction,
             adaptive conformal prediction, conformal PID control, and
             Multistep-ahead conformal prediction.
